metadata.name: The Last Breath
metadata.description:
In gardens, where the roses sigh and weep,  
Their petals fall, as mortal spirits leap,  
And with each breath of sweet, ephemeral breeze,  
In floral arms, we find our souls at ease.

___________

A collection of digitally edited ai artwork that explores the delicate and profound connection between humanity and the natural world, specifically through the lens of death and rebirth.
